						<div class="entry" id="entry_12345">
							
								<div class="col entry_right full">
																		<h1 class="title-news">
																				Cilantro and Avocado Pesto
									</h1>
																

							

								<div class="comments_datetime relative">
									
										
													<p>
														
															
															
														

														
															<br/>
														

														<span class="posted-and-updated">
															
First Posted: 10/27/2011  4:55 pm<span class="vborder-dashed margin_0_5">&nbsp;</span>Updated: 01/12/2012 11:37 am																
																
															
														</span>
													</p>
												
										
									<a href="?view=print" rel="nofollow" class="absolute print-link"></a>
								</div>
                                            					<div class="read_more_top v05"></div>
			            		
                                                
						<div class="clear"></div>

                        
        						                            

								<div class="clear_first"></div>

								
								

									<div id="follow_tags" data-beacon='{"p":{"mnid":"follow_tags"}}' class="read_more with_verticals clearfix">
										<div class="float_left follow_tags_headline normal_weight">
											<div class="float_left margin_right_3 arial_14">Read more</div>
											<img src="/images/bignews/follow-arrow.png" width="8" height="12" class="margin_right_3 padding_top_2" />
											<div class="clear"></div>
										</div>
                                                                            <div class="float_left follow_tags_cont">
									
									<a href="/kitchendaily"> KitchenDaily News</a>
                                                                        </div>
									</div>

							

							
								<div class="entry_body_text news_design_b">
<div id="ad_wrapper_sponsored_logo"></div>
			
			
	
	
	


		
	
	


			<p><!--[if IE]><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="screen" href="css/v/recipe-ie.css"  /><![endif]-->
<div itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Recipe" class="recipe-gadget">
	<h1 itemprop="name" style="display:none;">Cilantro and Avocado Pesto</h1>
	<div class="image-container">
				<img itemprop="image" class="recipe-image" src="http://o.aolcdn.com/dims-global/dims3/12AB/resize/456x342/http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/70309b42784df8c17a9d9de500ae720e/cilantro-and-avocado-pesto_456X342.jpg" alt="Cilantro and Avocado Pesto" />
				<div class="recipe-image-credit">Ray Kachatorian</div>
						<div class="credits">
			<span class="provided">Provided by: <a itemprop="author" class="provider" href=/curtis-stone-recipes/>Curtis Stone</a></span>
						<a href="/curtis-stone-recipes/"><img class="logo" src="http://o.aolcdn.com/os/living-food/provider-images/curtis-stone.gif" alt="" /></a>
					</div>
	</div>

	<div class="info group">

	
		<span class="cook-time">
			<span class="total"><time itemprop="totalTime" datetime="PT16M">16 mins</time> total</span>
			<span class="prep"><time itemprop="prepTime" datetime="PT15M">15 mins</time> prep</span>
		</span>

		
		<span class="options">
			<button class="enter-fullscreen">Full Screen</button>
			<form class="servings" action="">
				<input itemprop="recipeYield" id="serving-number" type="number" value="4" />
				<label for="serving-number">Servings</label>
				<input type="submit" value="Submit" style="display:none;" />
			</form>
		</span>
	</div>

	
	<div class="instructions group">
		<div class="ingredients">
			<h1>Ingredients</h1>
			<div>
				<ul>
				<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement volume"><span class="value">1 1/2</span> <span class="unit">cups </span></span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name">(lightly packed) fresh <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/cilantro/557/">cilantro</a> leaves</span></li>
<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement volume"><span class="value">1/2</span> <span class="unit">cup </span></span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name">freshly grated <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/parmesan/1778/">Parmesan</a> <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/cheese/499/">cheese</a></span></li>
<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement volume"><span class="value">1/2</span> <span class="unit">cup </span></span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name"><a href="/encyclopedia/definition/pine-nut/1865/">pine nuts</a>, <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/toast/2494/">toasted</a></span></li>
<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement quantity"><span class="value">1</span> </span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name"><a href="/encyclopedia/definition/garlic/1008/">garlic</a> <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/clove/575/">clove</a></span></li>
<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement volume"><span class="value">1/4</span> <span class="unit">cup </span></span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name">extra-virgin <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/olive-oil/1708/">olive oil</a></span></li>
<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement quantity"><span class="value">1</span> </span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name">ripe <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/avocado/119/">avocado</a>, peeled and pitted</span></li>
<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement quantity"><span class="value"></span> </span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name">Fresh <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/lime/1415/">lime</a> juice</span></li>
<li itemprop="ingredients" itemscope><span itemprop="amount" class="measurement quantity"><span class="value"></span> </span> <span itemprop="name" class="ingredient-name"><a href="/encyclopedia/definition/salts/2123/">Salt</a> and freshly ground black <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/pepper/1826/">pepper</a></span></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div itemprop="recipeInstructions" class="directions">
			<h1>Directions</h1>

			<div>
				<ul>
				<li>Grind the cilantro, Parmesan cheese, pine nuts, and garlic with a mortar and pestle until a smooth paste forms. If you don&rsquo;t have a mortar and pestle, use a food processor instead. Slowly add the olive oil, grinding until a smooth <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/sauces/2148/">sauce</a> forms. Add the avocado and grind until smooth and fully mixed into the sauce. Season the <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/pesto/1834/">pesto</a> to <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/tasting/2447/">taste</a> with the lime juice, salt, and pepper.</li>
<li>Press a sheet of plastic wrap directly onto the surface of the pesto and <a href="/encyclopedia/definition/refrigeration/2028/">refrigerate</a> until ready to serve.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
				<footer>
